nes would be also valuable for studies on further rodent-borne viruses, such as orthopox- and arenaviruses.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Eckerle, Isabella", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lenk, Matthias", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ulrich, Rainer", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/108dcf7e3d5622e79a3a3716fefa9765", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/37c27b014a792ed094c3c71c95a08e3fa7d039f58da891091d5da3f2cd0cecac", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/7FU7QF9T", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/7FU7QF9T", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/033eb5ce9ba1b709535e55aa763ca12a!/b112147-114613", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "951-967", "title": "Viruses", "volume": "6"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/108dcf7e3d5622e79a3a3716fefa9765"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:7FU7QF9T"}, {"identifier": "10.3390/v6030951"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13491384"}}]}}, "title": "More Novel Hantaviruses and Diversifying Reservoir Hosts \